{"TopicId":84729,"ForumId":46,"TopicTitle":"Mod description not wordwrapped correctly","CreatedByName":"Padishar","CreatedById":97386,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-09-16T10:51:14Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Padishar","CreatedById":97386,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-09-16T10:51:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI have just noticed (so I presume it is new) that the description text on my \u003Ca href=\u0022http://kerbal.curseforge.com/ksp-mods/220831-part-angle-display\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Emod page\u003C/a\u003E is not being wordwrapped correctly.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/0p9vbHv.jpg\u0022 alt=\u00220p9vbHv.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/czsuQsB.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022czsuQsB.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jadedcat","CreatedById":110413,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-09-16T19:26:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EIck. Thank you for the screenshots, I\u0027ll throw that at the engineers for a fix.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"vexx32","CreatedById":12283,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-09-16T21:03:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EWhoop, looks like someone set word-break: break-word; on the CSS -- or an equivalent property. Tsk, tsk. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Padishar","CreatedById":97386,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-09-17T12:11:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EYes, the \u0026lt;div class=\u0022project-description\u0022\u0026gt; element has this CSS:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003Ebody.body-projectsettings #site div#site-main #content .primary-content .project-description {\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003Eword-break: break-all;\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E}\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EShould be a trivial fix...\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"vexx32","CreatedById":12283,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-09-17T13:21:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI wonder why they had that set at all? It\u0027s only useful in a handful of cases anyway. :/\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jadedcat","CreatedById":110413,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-09-19T06:13:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI am told this issue should be fixed.\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}